      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation, this vehicle stands in pristine condition, reflecting a history of meticulous maintenance and discerning ownership. The exterior retains its showroom luster, while the interior remains entirely unblemished, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance and uncompromising reliability. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who demands nothing less than perfection.",
