    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm honestly sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love instantly. It's truly in pristine shape and ready for its new home. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
